'''中風帶'''（{{lang-en|Stroke Belt}}）是[[美國|美國]]一區域的非正式稱呼，主要範圍為[[美國東南部|美國東南部]]地區，該地區[[中風|中風]]等各種[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]的發病率異常高。

==地理範圍==
這個詞沒有明確的官方定義，一般是指東南部各州包括[[阿拉巴馬州|阿拉巴馬州]]、[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]、[[佐治亞州|佐治亞州]]、[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]、[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]、[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]、[[北卡羅來納州|北卡羅來納州]]、[[南卡羅來納州|南卡羅來納州]]和[[田納西州|田納西州]]<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.everydayhealth.com/stroke/stroke-risk-higher-in-southeastern-us.aspx | title=The 'Stroke Belt': Why is Stroke Risk Higher in the Southeast? | accessdate=2020-11-14 | archive-date=2020-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201021042/https://www.everydayhealth.com/stroke/stroke-risk-higher-in-southeastern-us.aspx | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在1980年，這9個州的年齡調整後的中風死亡率比美國全國平均水平高10％以上<ref name=Lessons>[http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/prof/heart/other/sb_spec.pdf Stroke Belt Initiative: Project Accomplishments and Lessons Learned] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/prof/heart/other/sb_spec.pdf |date=20081001162318 }}, National Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute, National Institutes of Health; reports on a conference that occurred in 1996</ref>。

尚未確定該區域中風發生率升高的原因，但已發現許多可能的促成因素，包括[[高血壓|高血壓]]、低社會經濟地位、飲食、文化生活方式、較低的醫療品質、[[吸煙|吸煙]]等<ref name=WornChildhood>{{cite journal |vauthors=Glymour MM, Avendaño M, Berkman LF |title=Is the 'stroke belt' worn from childhood?: risk of first stroke and state of residence in childhood and adulthood |journal=Stroke |volume=38 |issue=9 |pages=2415–21 |date=Sep 2007 |pmid=17673716 |doi=10.1161/STROKEAHA.107.482059 |url=http://stroke.ahajournals.org/cgi/content/full/38/9/2415 |access-date=2020-11-14 |archive-date=2010-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101002092855/http://stroke.ahajournals.org/cgi/content/full/38/9/2415 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

